11
00:00:45,378 --> 00:00:47,881
(Video audio: Seiichiro) Eh~ We are the Ise Group⸺

12
00:00:47,964 --> 00:00:50,800
Celebrating 150 years since founding

13
00:00:52,218 --> 00:00:54,387
Involved in our group⸺

14
00:00:54,471 --> 00:00:59,142
I would like to express my sincere gratitude to everyone around the world.

15
00:00:59,225 --> 00:01:04,105
Ise Group announced on January 23, 2025⸺

16
00:01:04,189 --> 00:01:09,069
We will hold a ceremony commemorating the 150th anniversary of our founding.

17
00:01:09,152 --> 00:01:13,823
(Yukiya) As the owner of the Ise family and the head of a large company⸺

18
00:01:14,365 --> 00:01:17,452
