20
00:01:20,413 --> 00:01:23,208
(Masayuki as a child) The very fact that you were born into this world was an accident.

21
00:01:23,291 --> 00:01:25,710
(Satoshi as a child) Accident Accident Accident Accident

22
00:01:25,794 --> 00:01:27,337
(Masayuki) Shit!

23
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:28,922
(Satoshi) Orya

24
00:01:29,756 --> 00:01:34,302
(Yukiya) Even if his hands are dirty, he still remains in his position⸺

25
00:01:34,385 --> 00:01:39,390
