26
00:01:40,683 --> 00:01:42,477
Seiichiro Ise

27
00:01:43,394 --> 00:01:46,064
devil living in the darkness

28
00:01:48,441 --> 00:01:50,276
Because of you, my mother...

29
00:02:02,705 --> 00:02:04,499
(Yukiya) To the bottom of the abyss⸺

30
00:02:05,917 --> 00:02:07,627
