114
00:10:46,145 --> 00:10:47,396
I probably can't eat it.

115
00:10:50,441 --> 00:10:53,027
-(Yukiya) Delicious-(Saori) Is it delicious? it was good

116
00:10:57,406 --> 00:10:58,949
