What do you know about my mother?

264
00:24:02,858 --> 00:24:04,234
forever⸺

265
00:24:05,402 --> 00:24:08,363
What kind of thoughts did you have in protecting that place?

266
00:24:14,578 --> 00:24:17,164
Anyone would be fine for you

267
00:24:18,999 --> 00:24:22,210
Anyone who listens to what is convenient

268
00:24:25,005 --> 00:24:30,427
I guess he took advantage of people's weaknesses to satisfy his own pleasure.

269
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:33,638
To you⸺

270
00:24:35,849 --> 00:24:39,102
Do you understand the feelings of people who cannot resist?

271
00:24:48,445 --> 00:24:49,988
(Seiichiro) To Saori⸺

272
00:24:51,907 --> 00:24:55,076
I've never given him money to meet him.

273
00:24:57,245 --> 00:24:58,288
Huh?

274
00:24:59,789 --> 00:25:02,584
(Seiichiro) It wasn't that kind of relationship.

275
00:25:25,023 --> 00:25:26,691
every night…

276
00:25:28,902 --> 00:25:30,737
I want to meet you⸺

277
00:25:32,197 --> 00:25:34,908
I still think

278
00:25:38,578 --> 00:25:42,415
She is my only...

279
00:25:43,375 --> 00:25:47,170
was the only light

280
00:25:53,468 --> 00:25:56,471
We met at the university's astronomy club.

281
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:05,272
Saori gave a ray of light to my life.

282
00:26:10,068 --> 00:26:11,778
Only when I'm with her⸺

283
00:26:12,904 --> 00:26:16,157
I forgot that I was a member of the Ise family.

284
00:26:18,702 --> 00:26:20,036
How many times⸺

285
00:26:21,746 --> 00:26:24,708
Did you really want to be together?

286
00:26:35,427 --> 00:26:38,388
Kyoko could see everything.

287
00:26:40,140 --> 00:26:44,603
That guy started harassing Matsushima Denki...

288
00:26:47,355 --> 00:26:49,816
Saori told me

289
00:26:53,320 --> 00:26:56,448
(Saori) Let's stop seeing each other again.

290
00:26:58,950 --> 00:27:02,120
(Seiichiro) If it's money, I'll do something about it.

291
00:27:02,203 --> 00:27:03,496
different

292
00:27:06,166 --> 00:27:10,712
Don't think that everything can be solved with money.

293
00:27:13,089 --> 00:27:14,633
Such a relationship⸺

294
00:27:16,343 --> 00:27:18,261
I was wrong from the beginning

295
00:27:28,897 --> 00:27:30,565
all⸺

296
00:27:32,609 --> 00:27:34,819
it's my responsibility

297
00:27:39,407 --> 00:27:44,454
Because I couldn't forget Saori

298
00:27:47,707 --> 00:27:52,128
In the end, it was because of the harassment at that time.

299
00:27:53,171 --> 00:27:56,925
Matsushima Electric's management suddenly turned upside down.

300
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:00,845
Seven years later⸺

301
00:28:02,263 --> 00:28:04,766
I ended up going bankrupt.

302
00:28:10,730 --> 00:28:16,277
(Yukiya/Saori in childhood) ♪ Twinkle Hikaru

303
00:28:16,361 --> 00:28:20,990
♪ The star of the sky

304
00:28:21,074 --> 00:28:26,913
♪ Don't blink

305
00:28:26,996 --> 00:28:32,127
♪ I'm watching everyone

306
00:28:34,379 --> 00:28:36,131
-(Saori) Yukiya-(Yukiya) Yeah?

307
00:28:37,507 --> 00:28:42,011
Even if this factory becomes part of the Ise Group⸺

308
00:28:42,804 --> 00:28:48,560
The time and memories spent here will remain in my heart forever.

309
00:28:51,104 --> 00:28:54,065
The passion and soul poured into this place⸺

310
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,818
Everything won't disappear

311
00:28:59,863 --> 00:29:03,116
So... it's okay

312
00:29:07,954 --> 00:29:10,665
(Seiichiro) I heard that Matsushima Electric was going to go bankrupt⸺

313
00:29:12,083 --> 00:29:14,919
I just want to prevent that at all costs⸺

314
00:29:15,003 --> 00:29:17,046
claimed to be an acquisition

315
00:29:19,382 --> 00:29:20,633
but⸺

316
00:29:22,051 --> 00:29:25,555
There was no way Kyoko would allow something like that to happen.

317
00:29:27,182 --> 00:29:28,558
well…

318
00:29:32,687 --> 00:29:35,148
My mother was fired...

319
00:29:36,941 --> 00:29:40,945
It was a condition for us to acquire Matsushima Electric.

320
00:29:43,656 --> 00:29:45,742
So⸺

321
00:29:47,368 --> 00:29:50,747
You adopted me out of guilt.

322
00:29:51,706 --> 00:29:54,542
(Seiichiro) I think I've done everything I can.

323
00:29:59,631 --> 00:30:01,341
Don't be silly!

324
00:30:02,467 --> 00:30:06,638
My memories of that house are hell.

325
00:30:06,721 --> 00:30:07,764
(Seiichiro) Ah...

326
00:30:10,433 --> 00:30:13,061
Hah...I think I'm sorry.

327
00:30:13,144 --> 00:30:16,356
Ha ha ha ha...

328
00:30:16,439 --> 00:30:20,568
Every time I look at you, Saori's shadow crosses my mind⸺

329
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:23,112
was not accepted

330
00:30:24,322 --> 00:30:27,033
I don't know how to approach you⸺

331
00:30:27,116 --> 00:30:29,035
I couldn't take it anymore

332
00:30:29,118 --> 00:30:32,205
Ha ha ha ha...

333
00:30:32,914 --> 00:30:36,125
Yukiya... ha...

334
00:30:36,209 --> 00:30:39,003
Ha ha ha ha...

335
00:30:39,087 --> 00:30:40,588
Yukiya

336
00:30:43,424 --> 00:30:44,801
(Yukiya) So?

337
00:30:45,885 --> 00:30:47,971
Do you think you can just apologize?

338
00:30:50,098 --> 00:30:52,767
I have no reason to forgive you.

339
00:30:53,893 --> 00:30:55,019
I understand

340
00:30:56,646 --> 00:31:01,109
You will continue to be punished until you die.

341
00:31:01,818 --> 00:31:03,653
Huh...

342
00:31:03,736 --> 00:31:05,405
That's my intention

343
00:31:06,364 --> 00:31:09,492
That's why I want you to do this...

344
00:31:09,576 --> 00:31:14,455
No matter what you say, I'm not going to forgive you.

345
00:31:17,709 --> 00:31:19,377
I was convinced

346
00:31:21,754 --> 00:31:24,424
You're the devil after all

347
00:31:24,966 --> 00:31:31,347
A devil who cannot think of people as human beings just like himself.

348
00:31:35,852 --> 00:31:38,146
An excuse for someone like that⸺

349
00:31:38,229 --> 00:31:41,608
I feel sorry for myself who came to ask Nokoko.

350
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:52,619
And...

351
00:31:54,495 --> 00:31:56,039
Don't glorify it

352
00:31:58,541 --> 00:32:01,210
Mom always said that

353
00:32:01,294 --> 00:32:03,755
“Don’t be obsessed with money”

354
00:32:05,548 --> 00:32:07,884
“For such poor people⸺”

355
00:32:08,718 --> 00:32:11,638
“There’s nothing attractive about it.”

356
00:32:20,104 --> 00:32:23,232
(Sound of door opening and closing)

357
00:33:53,698 --> 00:33:58,411
cry)

358
00:34:06,878 --> 00:34:08,171
(Yukiya) Mother

359
00:34:09,505 --> 00:34:10,798
I...

360
00:34:12,467 --> 00:34:14,385
I've been lonely for a long time

361
00:34:18,222 --> 00:34:20,141
Why suicide?

362
00:34:20,641 --> 00:34:23,019
It would be better if we ran away together

363
00:34:25,229 --> 00:34:27,273
I don't need money

364
00:34:29,067 --> 00:34:33,070
I wish I could live peacefully with my mother⸺

365
00:34:34,781 --> 00:34:35,656
That's all...

366
00:34:39,202 --> 00:34:40,369
(sound of tapping on desk)

367
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:48,711
(sound of tapping)

368
00:34:54,717 --> 00:34:56,385
Huh...

369
00:35:00,515 --> 00:35:02,058
Huh...

370
00:35:10,441 --> 00:35:14,654
(Erika) Well, your father-in-law has become useless.

371
00:35:16,739 --> 00:35:18,574
It's an empty shell

372
00:35:36,926 --> 00:35:40,680
Maybe it's a good idea to make it easier.

373
00:35:40,763 --> 00:35:42,557
About your father-in-law

374
00:36:14,172 --> 00:36:16,215
knock)

375
00:36:32,815 --> 00:36:36,944
(door chime)

376
00:36:44,410 --> 00:36:47,204
(door chime)

377
00:36:54,587 --> 00:36:56,589
‪♪～

378
00:37:28,704 --> 00:37:32,166
(door chime)

379
00:37:40,675 --> 00:37:41,884
(Yukiya) Hanaho

380
00:37:42,510 --> 00:37:46,264
-(Hanaho) Yukiya-kun, help me-(Yukiya) Ah...

381
00:37:46,347 --> 00:37:48,057
(sound of glass breaking)

382
00:37:55,982 --> 00:37:57,984
‪～♪

383
00:38:13,040 --> 00:38:17,503
(Erika) There is no one who can interfere with us anymore.

384
00:38:17,586 --> 00:38:19,922
(Yukiya) My mother didn't commit suicide.

385
00:38:20,006 --> 00:38:21,132
(Saori) Please, please go home already.

386
00:38:21,215 --> 00:38:22,216
please

387
00:38:22,300 --> 00:38:23,843
(screams)

388
00:38:23,926 --> 00:38:25,845
 (Yukiya) I don't care what happens now.

389
00:38:25,928 --> 00:38:27,930
I won't forgive you
